ImageSearcher
Deprecated. use GenericFastImageSearcher instead 

public class CEDDImageSearcher
extends GenericImageSearcher

Provides a faster way of searching based on byte arrays instead of Strings. The method CEDD.getByteArrayRepresentation() is used to generate the signature of the descriptor much faster. First tests have shown that this implementation is up to 4 times faster than the implementation based on strings (for 120,000 images)

User: Mathias Lux, mathias@juggle.at Date: 12.03.2010 Time: 13:21:50
